-Ah, ¿no?

716
00:51:16,200 --> 00:51:17,400
-Por favor.

717
00:51:21,360 --> 00:51:23,040
Espera un momento, por favor.

718
00:51:26,280 --> 00:51:27,280
(TOSE)

719
00:51:59,720 --> 00:52:01,400
