738
00:54:13,760 --> 00:54:16,400
¡Mamá! ¡Mamá, corre!

739
00:54:17,840 --> 00:54:18,840
Javi.

740
00:54:19,600 --> 00:54:20,600
Javi, cariño.

741
00:54:30,880 --> 00:54:32,560
Mónica, llama al 112, corre.

742
00:54:33,760 --> 00:54:34,760
Soy médico.

743
00:54:36,280 --> 00:54:38,960
